<section class="about-hero" aria-labelledby="about-page-title">
  <div class="site-container about-hero__content">
    <span class="about-kicker">About</span>

    <h1 id="about-page-title" class="about-hero__title">
      A public-interest investigative and educational project
    </h1>

    <p class="about-hero__lead">
      The Accountability Report Podcast is hosted by Sarai Hannah Ajai. It examines
      documented concerns and accountability questions affecting consumers, small
      operators, and the public record.
    </p>
  </div>
