<section class="about-body" aria-labelledby="about-overview-title">
  <div class="site-container about-body__grid">
    <article class="about-copy">
      <h2 id="about-overview-title">
        Hosted by Sarai Hannah Ajai
      </h2>

      <p>
        Sarai Hannah Ajai is the host and founder of The Accountability Report Podcast,
        a public-interest investigative podcast focused on fraud awareness, identity theft
        documentation, digital misuse, consumer protection concerns, and accountability
        reporting. The podcast is designed to review documented concerns, public records
        where available, consumer protection pathways, and practical steps for preserving
        evidence.
      </p>

      <h2>
        Editorial mission
      </h2>

      <p>
        The podcast reviews documented concerns, public records where available, consumer
        protection processes, and practical steps for preserving evidence and reporting
        suspected fraud. Coverage is framed carefully and factually, with attention to what
        is reported versus what has been confirmed.
      </p>

      <h2>
        Sources and selection
      </h2>

      <p>
        Each episode draws on publicly available records, listener-submitted documentation,
        published agency guidance, and editorial review. Stories are selected for their
        broader relevance to identity protection, digital account security, intellectual
        property integrity, and consumer rights.
      </p>

      <h2>
        Scope and limitations
      </h2>

      <p>
        The podcast does not provide legal, financial, medical, or cybersecurity professional
        advice. Allegations referenced on the show are discussed as reported concerns unless
        confirmed by official findings.
      </p>

      <aside class="about-note" aria-label="Host note">
        <strong>Host:</strong>
        <span>
          Sarai Hannah Ajai produces and hosts The Accountability Report Podcast as an
          independent public-interest project focused on transparency, documentation, and
          consumer awareness.
        </span>
      </aside>
    </article>

